{"tid":1534701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣方向建議］加強向美國搖擺州宣傳","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:34:50.000Z","uid":316996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0f37db94b5d7e44ac151dd5d55b8fa9021aee1","tid":1534701,"uid":316996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:43:09.000Z","msg":"小弟係一個讀政治嘅學生，分享一吓純國際政治角度嘅淺見：<br />\n　　香港本身就係中國同埋國際之間利益角力＋互利而扶持起嚟嘅國際金融中心，係國際政經嘅角力場之一，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家要跟住大時代嚟爭取最大嘅可能！</span></strong>美國係唯一真正可以透過行動實際影響到中國高層決策嘅國家，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">我覺得大家可以擺部份精力去針對美國總統選舉搖擺州（swing state）嚟做公眾外交（對外宣傳）。</span></strong><br />\n　　美國總統杜林普（Donald Trump）近排多咗關注香港嘅抗爭，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">除咗係因為美中貿易戰嘅談判，背後更加重要嘅原因係2020年11月3號嘅連任選情。</span></strong>佢嘅最大對手民主黨係比較偏左，雖然對中國嘅外交同埋經貿政策唔會咁強硬，但始終會比較堅持民主、自由、法治等等嘅價值觀。<br />\n　　普遍美國人民對香港嘅抗爭會有人道同情，加上美中競爭嘅反中民情，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">民主黨之前就有企喺民主高地嚟批評杜林普對香港嘅冷淡（當然係為咗選舉），所以杜林普好大機會有因為呢點而多咗關注香港（至少令到中國唔會直接出解放軍）。</span></strong><br />\n　　「搖擺州」係指冇一邊政黨候選人有鐵票優勢贏到選舉人票嘅州，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">呢啲州係共和黨同埋民主黨總統候選人嘅主要爭取目標，</span></strong>因為贏咗呢啲州嘅選舉人票係好重要。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我哋跟住睇吓2016年美國總統選舉嘅搖擺州</div><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1U3NvOL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1U3NvOL.jpg&h=1405adce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 　　杜林普喺2016年嘅民選票數62,984,828（46.1%）雖然輸咗俾希拉莉65,853,514（48.2%），但最尾以選舉人票（304比227）贏咗大選，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">當中嘅一個關鍵就係搖擺州嘅選情。</span></strong>特別俄亥俄州同埋佛羅里達州係最大嘅搖擺州，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1964年以嚟贏咗俄州嘅人就贏總統，1996年以嚟贏咗佛州嘅人就贏總統。<br />\n　　我建議最基本嘅可以打人道牌＋價值牌，用抗爭者俾警察打＋捍衛自由民主法治嘅文宣，同時加上「五大訴求」嘅目標，向呢啲搖擺州嘅出名人物、媒體、非政府組織等等嘅Twitter、Facebook、Instagram、Snapchat同埋Email宣傳。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMROZHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMROZHw.jpg&h=4354960b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n　　<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">咁樣做嘅目的係為咗儘量吸引搖擺州人民嘅關注，希望間接令到杜林普多啲機會更加重視香港（特別係瞭解五大訴求嘅民主運動），從而更加對中國施壓。因為佢係短期之內最有力左右大局嘅人，發揮公眾外交（對外宣傳）嘅最大效果。</span></strong><br />\n　　如果想深入啲宣傳，可以根據每個州嘅選民特質嚟針對宣傳；又或者打經濟牌，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">分析香港對各方相互經濟利益嘅利害關係，如果香港唔掂對佢有咩影響，希望令佢意識到香港係有同各方利益綁埋一齊。</span></strong><br />\n　　另外杜林普嘅外交戰略有個「印太戰略」(Indo-Pacific strategy)嘅概念，主要係嚟制衡中國嘅「一帶一路」，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">重要成員有美國、印度、日本、澳洲</span></strong>，大家亦都可以考慮多啲向呢啲國家宣傳，睇最近局勢特別係澳洲。（老實講歐盟可以做嘅嘢作用唔大）<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">最尾分享臺灣數位外交協會關於公眾外交嘅介紹俾大家睇吓</div><br />\n網路數位外交嘅重要同埋低成本：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TaiwanDigitalDiplomacy/posts/801605983547701/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTaiwanDigitalDiplomacy%2Fposts%2F801605983547701%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=1125a7ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TaiwanDigitalDiplomacy/posts/801605983547701/</a><br />\n用「框架理論」嚟做公眾外交：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TaiwanDigitalDiplomacy/posts/809902022718097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTaiwanDigitalDiplomacy%2Fposts%2F809902022718097&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=fd90a7c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TaiwanDigitalDiplomacy/posts/809902022718097</a><br />\n公眾外交嘅總結介紹：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TaiwanDigitalDiplomacy/posts/836900850018214/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTaiwanDigitalDiplomacy%2Fposts%2F836900850018214%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=0a5d76f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TaiwanDigitalDiplomacy/posts/836900850018214/</a>"},{"pid":"2c2e493aa8729bff299daccd531fee5169f0e52f","tid":1534701,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9a67cef26012925a3b931e315308209de438e1c","tid":1534701,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ba734064a3cd08a759b09ab06106873a3e85204","tid":1534701,"uid":287449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"咁就記得上twitter文宣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借位宣傳<br />\n侵侵同d外國人都冇加你fb同ig，點知你想要咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再係facebook同ig自己圍爐打飛機啦，一齊黎開始國際戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個tweet幾秒鐘，一蚊都唔洗，又唔洗綁電話，安全又快捷，快d一齊轉用twitter啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">twitter文宣共識TG</span>： </span></strong><a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=45414838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n內有twitter詳細教學，開個account唔洗3分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文唔好驚比人笑？唔洗驚，國際文宣谷幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🔥<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>反送中 國際文宣谷link</strong></span></span>🔥<br />\n國際 Channel ：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo_int&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=5c819284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int</a>"},{"pid":"2e04e78b5e94c208ae68c0a9b47d83264ac81490","tid":1534701,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月重鎚出擊加拿大<br />\n10月26日大選<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jm8510o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJm8510o.png&h=19a117eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3afe40e62a6beca74f31ebe1d85beebddd2733b","tid":1534701,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:00:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"913bde483cb739cc170cf58c498887b1d2f9e255","tid":1534701,"uid":145979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"除左大國，小國有無效，之前有巴打提過印尼，仲有一帶一路國家，例如斯里蘭卡，已經差緊中國錢，要租借碼頭還錢。不斷灌輸中國入侵呢個信息比全世界，各國政要取向越趨排華，先可以反哺到香港。就像小國繼續同中國合作，幫佢地爭取議價能力，燒下中共後欄都係好事。"},{"pid":"23f50c9c2aaa961bf1fe35e5e4e95ea75ccfbf51","tid":1534701,"uid":316996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"913bde483cb739cc170cf58c498887b1d2f9e255","tid":1534701,"uid":145979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"除左大國，小國有無效，之前有巴打提過印尼，仲有一帶一路國家，例如斯里蘭卡，已經差緊中國錢，要租借碼頭還錢。不斷灌輸中國入侵呢個信息比全世界，各國政要取向越趨排華，先可以反哺到香港。就像小國繼續同中國合作，幫佢地爭取議價能力，燒下中共後欄都係好事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"長期嚟講都得嘅，如果呢個模式得，之後可以考慮成立一個公眾外交／數位外交嘅網路組織，日常化咁去做對外宣傳、溝通同埋合作嘅工作（參考臺灣）。短期嚟講一帶一路嘅細國應該幫助唔大喇，佢哋應該唔多重視人道牌＋價值牌，經濟牌又未咁快發揮到大效果。"},{"pid":"a96d0d2800e71da7ef9b7bf1092220f6502f1d40","tid":1534701,"uid":79602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba2ab80aaf34f98956ed44f35083c9a46ba257e6","tid":1534701,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"老老實實 如果打人道牌嘅話點會投trump 大愛嘅實投返民主黨 親hispanics &amp; blacks<br />\n<br />\n想講警暴嘅話... black lives matter 都係反警暴 但撐警嘅多數係republican<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896f2b13587e80e431662457269f987f2a837ee3","tid":1534701,"uid":316996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba2ab80aaf34f98956ed44f35083c9a46ba257e6","tid":1534701,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"老老實實 如果打人道牌嘅話點會投trump 大愛嘅實投返民主黨 親hispanics &amp; blacks<br />\n<br />\n想講警暴嘅話... black lives matter 都係反警暴 但撐警嘅多數係republican<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:25:28.000Z","msg":"你啱，我嘅目的唔係想影響美國總統選舉嘅選情／介入政黨偏好，主要都係想令Trump感受多啲選情壓力，佢都要做嘢爭取多啲搖擺州選民嘅支持，短期內（至少仲有選舉壓力之前）希望佢搭配埋貿易戰談判對中國多啲外交施壓"},{"pid":"9e4dcd4ba1940129bba536d24c92c1ee4b44e57d","tid":1534701,"uid":316996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"*你啱，不過我嘅目的..."}]}